post有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>奇怪就係一個 CE 中文 英文 3 會比一個DSE 中文 英文 同樣係 3嘅人好 不論係文法 用字 文體 講什至聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一邊最高係7<br />\n一邊係6<br />\n咁ce英文3同dse英文4差唔多<br />\n咁好過3係好正常"},{"pid":"edb0bd8a537bd1d699ed287258a0e0a28a110902","tid":645360,"uid":38359,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e6c21f183b161fb5f0dc9f98ae05c5559eb84d1e","tid":645360,"uid":108450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6d6b29f5033e4970c9dd212dd4f30e60f82615","tid":645360,"uid":106468,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"Phy Chem Bio 3科一定係DSE 無討論空間<br />\n依個post有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"奇怪就係一個 CE 中文 英文 3 會比一個DSE 中文 英文 同樣係 3嘅人好 不論係文法 用字 文體 講什至聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"先唔講2個考試scale唔同  一個6分滿分 一個7分滿分<br />\n<br />\n考得ce既人都已經有一定歷史 dse就岩岩先開始 同學考完唔會好耐<br />\n就算大家都係CE出黎 00 年既人同05年既比較 一個係考完試有多5年時間係社會上 大學上浸淫過一排 一個就岩岩考完 我諗就算佢地同分，00年既考生經過五年，點都會有所進步，會比岩岩考完試既05年既考生好。<br />\n<br />\n不過我諗樓主都係覺得自己ce攞3 係十幾年之後同dse雞比，覺得自己language好過dse level 3既考生 所以覺得dse既人就係垃圾就係差既老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adde081810a12bbe4c4489e74a55f249f293d6c","tid":645360,"uid":103732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6c21f183b161fb5f0dc9f98ae05c5559eb84d1e","tid":645360,"uid":108450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6d6b29f5033e4970c9dd212dd4f30e60f82615","tid":645360,"uid":106468,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"Phy Chem Bio 3科一定係DSE 無討論空間<br />\n依個post有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"奇怪就係一個 CE 中文 英文 3 會比一個DSE 中文 英文 同樣係 3嘅人好 不論係文法 用字 文體 講什至聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:40:28.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\nCE中英拎3or above既比率唔夠4成<br />\n但DSE中英拎3 or above就多過5成<br />\n究竟係班00後語文能力好咗...定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}